{
  "id": "adv_event_2208_01_03",
  "title": "マリンブルー\nの憂鬱",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_train-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの四人で合宿、ねえ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir's four-person training camp‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.9544898032999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.1678231557
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "合宿か、久しぶりだね。でも、今回必要ある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A training camp‚ huh? It's been a while. But is it necessary this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1678231557,
      "endTime": 11.475600846599999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.6689341228
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんですか～。先輩方に足りないもの\nそれは、夏の素敵な体験なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you saying~? What our senpais lack\nis a wonderful summer experience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6689341228,
      "endTime": 18.392607752500002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.585941124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "お二人ともず～～っと\n仕事とレッスンの毎日ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you have been constantly\nbusy with work and lessons‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.585941124,
      "endTime": 23.300181484299998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあいい夏の曲なんて作れる訳ありませんよ？\nね？　愛ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ there's no way you can create a great summer song‚ you know?\nRight‚ Ai-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5001814843,
      "endTime": 28.815759754299997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.009092935
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　……う、うん、そうだね！\n先輩方、もっと夏を楽しまないといけません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Y-Yeah‚ you're right!\nOur senpais need to enjoy summer more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.009092935,
      "endTime": 36.0538548789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2405217172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "それは、そうかもしれないけど……\n私達、今どこに向かってるの？　近所の海岸とか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be true‚ but…\nWhere are we heading right now? To a nearby beach or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2405217172,
      "endTime": 43.94346962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1501362485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1501362485,
      "endTime": 45.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6666666667,
      "endTime": 46.780113220000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと……貴方突然、何言ってるの！？\nそんな所、気軽に行ける訳ないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait a minute… What are you suddenly saying!?\nWe can't just casually go to a place like that‚ can we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9666666667,
      "endTime": 53.6904694557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "ていうか、電車で行けないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ we can't go there by train‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9,
      "endTime": 56.6237189293,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ご安心下さい、この電車は\nちゃ～んと空港に向かってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry‚ this train\nis headed straight to the airport.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8,
      "endTime": 61.614091292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、{user}さんも了承済ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ {user} has already approved it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8333333333,
      "endTime": 65.4711564858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "新曲を書かないと、ツアーが出来ないわ！\nそのためには気高く沖縄で合宿するしかないのよっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to write a new song‚ or we won't be able to go on tour!\nFor that‚ we have no choice but to hold our heads high and have a training camp in Okinawa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8,
      "endTime": 75.4667028383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_train-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "――って、莉央さんが言ってました\nと伝えたら簡単でした～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I told what Rio-san said‚\nand it was easy~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8,
      "endTime": 81.9817754577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方、そこまでして合宿を組んでくれたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You went to such lengths to plan this training camp‚ didn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1666666667,
      "endTime": 86.5690703074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "いだだだだだ先輩のこぶしがこめかみにめり込む～\n表情とやってることがミスマッチですぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san's fist is digging into my temple~\nYour expression doesn't match what you're doing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7666666667,
      "endTime": 95.9933465015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕、旅行の準備、何もしてないんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't done anything to prepare for the trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1666666667,
      "endTime": 99.9579364936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、それは向こうでなんとかなりますよ！\n国内ですし、なんでも売ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you'll be fine! We're going within the country‚\nand they sell everything there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2,
      "endTime": 106.1068706825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、海なんてどこも同じでしょ？\n星見の海でも良かったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But aren't all beaches the same?\nEven Hoshimi's beach would have been okay‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3,
      "endTime": 111.39666675730001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、沖縄をナメてはいけません\nマリンブルーの海は最高ですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san‚ don't underestimate Okinawa.\nThe marine blue sea is fantastic!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6,
      "endTime": 118.4964340107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "一流アイドルらしく、豪華なリゾートホテルで\n夏を満喫しながら優雅に新曲の構想を練るべきです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As top idols‚ we should come up with our new song ideas\nwhile enjoying summer at a luxurious resort hotel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7,
      "endTime": 127.0918322093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "豪華なリゾートホテル……優雅……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Luxurious resort hotel… elegant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3,
      "endTime": 131.0424717426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
